column5: looks windy on friday      but packing and getting ready to go
Figures.... Sunny for Tuesday. guess we'll see what the real weather is when we get there.
I think a few of the guys will sit and party, more then fish with weather like that
I'd have to say that that forecast lloks good for the weekend walleye fishing. Nice walleye chop.
I notice today is absolutely beautiful and would be a great day to fish BOQ  Joey
I agree Joey. Such a nice day, why are we inside working

saturday the winds not too bad and sunday a little better but friday, looks like a right off, I should bring a surf board...and it will most likely take part of saturday for the wave to calm down  oh and I am going there thursday night..so friday is the first big day
Yep beauty day out there today! Hope they're a bit off on the weather report...our Charter is Friday! Guess I'd better give Lloyd my cell # in case he calls it off.
Looks like Saturday is going to be "The" day to me... but I don't know crap from Shinola about Walleyed Pickeral fishin'.
yeah saturday is looking like the day......  I'm real glad the picture with you and the truck, is real small my poor eyes can barely make it out and that's a good thing
